    <h3>What is Simple Settler?</h3>

    <p>Simple Settler is an app that can help you stay informed on the important things you need to connect and get started with when you move into a new city.</p>

    <p>Using Simple Settler is just like asking your friend or family for advice on how to get connected in a city that you will be staying in for the next few years – except instead of asking someone or finding information yourself in different places across the web, you have one platform that has all the information you need.</p>

    <h3>What are the ways I can use Simple Settler?</h3>

    <p>Browse categories among others such as Transport, Finance, Immigration, Jobs, Accommodation, Food and more.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Find articles such as how to get set up with a bank account, transport apps to download for your mobile device in your city, maximum amount of work hours required for an int’l student and we can go forever</li>
      <li>Save topics to your profile and read later what you need</li>
